=== Etymology ===
From Latin ''gaudium'' meaning "joy" via French.

== [[adjective]] ==
#being happy, joyful and lively.
#being bright and colorful.
#''Slang''. Homosexual male or female. (More often used for male)
#something that is bad or rubbish.

